                           Alien Breed 3D Patch                           ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~                  Copyright Team 17 Software Ltd. 1996This archive contains a freely available replacement for the mainexecutable file of Team17's Alien Breed 3D. The patch fixes the inabilityto activate the of 8 channel 'surround sound' during the game.As with other in-game options, the patch can be toggled on or off duringthe pause mode. Simply use the defined up and down keys to toggle.To patch the game, simply copy the file 'ABD.PK' to the same directoryon your floppy or hard disk where the original AB3D.PK file was located.***MAKE SURE YOU HAVE BACKED UP YOUR FLOPPY OR ORIGINAL ABD.PK FILE***8/2/96 Gareth Edwards, Webmaster. Team 17 Software Ltd.